the quality of the writing

01:44:05.290 --> 01:44:08.620
because he says he's
basically forgotten Arabic

01:44:08.620 --> 01:44:09.920
and his own language.

01:44:09.920 --> 01:44:12.890
So there's just this
hint of loss there.

01:44:12.890 --> 01:44:14.910
