a descendant of the prophet.

01:44:30.370 --> 01:44:35.070
He also gives a long
list of his teachers.

01:44:35.070 --> 01:44:44.050
And there are documents in other
parts of the Americas written

01:44:44.050 --> 01:44:51.540
