01:45:29.110 --> 01:45:34.620
And also the interpretation
of those.

01:45:34.620 --> 01:45:41.880
Because you know, there are
quite a few old documents

01:45:41.880 --> 01:45:47.910
and those need to be interpreted
by people who can do that.

01:45:47.910 --> 01:45:52.030
And it's not necessarily
scholars who can do that,

01:45:52.030 --> 01:45:55.720
