predecessor was a Muslim?

01:46:39.620 --> 01:46:44.280
Or that were actually practicing
Islam without the knowledge

01:46:44.280 --> 01:46:49.050
that their predecessor
was a Muslim?

01:46:49.050 --> 01:46:51.750
&gt;&gt; Dr. Sylviane Diuof: I
think there are probably both

01:46:51.750 --> 01:46:53.050
of those.

01:46:53.050 --> 01:46:58.620
The thing is that what we've
seen a few years ago is

01:46:58.620 --> 01:47:04.730
that people whose DNA was
for example said to be --

01:47:04.730 --> 01:47:09.620
because I have my
reservation about that --

01:47:09.620 --> 01:47:11.860
said to be Fulbe or Olsa.

01:47:11.860 --> 01:47:20.480
So people who are mostly
Muslims, then you know,

01:47:20.480 --> 01:47:25.580
some of the people
actually became Muslims,

01:47:25.580 --> 01:47:33.540
or Muslims today have
their DNA traced to check

01:47:33.540 --> 01:47:36.470
