01:47:36.470 --> 01:47:44.480
So it's kind of -- now you
know, again this is kind of --

01:47:44.480 --> 01:47:49.200
those are situations that are
a little iffy if you will.

01:47:49.200 --> 01:48:00.330
And religion, I don't know if
biology can give you any kind

01:48:00.330 --> 01:48:03.680
of way of becoming Muslims.

01:48:03.680 --> 01:48:06.230
I mean, to me it's
all complicated.

