history through textbook pages,

02:42:20.840 --> 02:42:25.400
maybe through some films in
class, a lot of lectures.

02:42:25.400 --> 02:42:28.820
I would say this is the first
time I was able to learn history

02:42:28.820 --> 02:42:32.970
in this kind of way and really
feel like connected to Omar.

02:42:32.970 --> 02:42:34.580
It wasn't just reading pages.

02:42:34.580 --> 02:42:38.790
I was so passionate about it
