02:47:14.360 --> 02:47:16.180
Because I'm not really
a history person,

02:47:16.180 --> 02:47:19.160
just to dig into the
history and make it a film,

02:47:19.160 --> 02:47:21.380
this is the first time
I've did it before.

02:47:21.380 --> 02:47:22.680
This is amazing.

02:47:22.680 --> 02:47:26.410
It was a very great experience,
