do you think can be done not

03:46:00.910 --> 03:46:04.540
through like the Library
of Congress in style

03:46:04.540 --> 03:46:08.880
and profession, but by a
community who wants to preserve

03:46:08.880 --> 03:46:13.070
that part of history and bring
it to the rest of the world?

03:46:13.070 --> 03:46:15.370
Thank you.

