have like, cameras, but it's not

03:46:48.460 --> 03:46:51.830
like an organized
like technology setup

03:46:51.830 --> 03:46:53.730
that we have in place now.

03:46:53.730 --> 03:46:56.720
&gt;&gt; David Reser: Well, aside from
the really high-end equipment

03:46:56.720 --> 03:47:00.540
