03:59:06.550 --> 03:59:07.850
To do my job correctly,

03:59:07.850 --> 03:59:09.830
I'm looking for authoritative
sources.

03:59:09.830 --> 03:59:13.500
So I was reading a lot of the
literature just to be able

03:59:13.500 --> 03:59:15.010
to catalog the materials.

03:59:15.010 --> 03:59:17.860
So in the process
of doing that --

03:59:17.860 --> 03:59:22.000
